    "name": "Sylph",
    "type": "alien",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Slyphs are descendants of species and creatures from the Material Plane that have strong connections to the Plane of Air, such as djinn. They can also arise in areas that have strong influences from the Plane of Air. Though sylphs can pass for other kinds of humanoids, they tend to be slender, and all have complex blue markings swirling across their skin. Sylphs are naturally reserved and they avoid attention."
        }
    ],
